WEBVTT

00:01.290 --> 00:03.690
Do not try what you're about to see at home.

00:03.860 --> 00:06.200
We're what you call experts.

00:07.710 --> 00:11.160
On this car-crazy episode of Mythbusters:

00:11.170 --> 00:13.000
The obscenity begins!

00:13.120 --> 00:15.890
Adam and Jamie think outside the box...

00:15.890 --> 00:17.060
Well, there's your problem.

00:17.060 --> 00:19.820
as they literally reinvent the wheel

00:19.820 --> 00:22.610
Our lives have officially become a cartoon.

00:22.610 --> 00:24.670
Testing the myth that square wheels

00:24.670 --> 00:26.070
will give you a smooth ride...

00:26.980 --> 00:29.640
provided you drive fast enough.

00:32.060 --> 00:34.450
Meanwhile, Kari, Tory, and Grant

00:34.540 --> 00:37.000
tackle a "Date Night" movie myth.

00:37.380 --> 00:39.230
Well, there's something you don't see every day.

00:39.230 --> 00:41.780
Can two cars stuck bumper to bumper...

00:41.780 --> 00:42.660
Let's do it.

00:42.660 --> 00:44.180
drive city streets...

00:44.180 --> 00:45.970
- I've got no steering! - Brakes! Brakes!

00:45.970 --> 00:47.990
cut corners...

00:48.270 --> 00:49.940
Can you believe we're getting paid to do this?

00:49.940 --> 00:51.980
and even do a 180 spin?

00:53.520 --> 00:54.520
So, yeah,

00:54.520 --> 00:56.960
that was pretty much the best date I've ever been on.

00:59.510 --> 01:01.630
Who are the mythbusters?

01:02.430 --> 01:03.240
Adam Savage...

01:05.940 --> 01:07.240
and Jamie Hyneman.

01:07.240 --> 01:09.910
Things are gonna start to get a little crazy in here.

01:09.910 --> 01:14.110
Between them, more than 30 years of special-effects experience.

01:14.120 --> 01:15.880
Together with Grant Imahara...

01:16.870 --> 01:18.030
Kari Byron...

01:18.350 --> 01:19.570
Hi, Grant!

01:19.570 --> 01:20.970
and Tory Belleci.

01:20.970 --> 01:21.680
Hit it!

01:22.040 --> 01:24.080
They don't just tell the myths,

01:24.440 --> 01:26.790
they put them to the test.

