In the ultimate square wheel finale,

35:37.450 --> 35:39.730
Jamie's got a dirty idea.

35:39.730 --> 35:40.990
Coming up on "Mythbusters"...

35:40.990 --> 35:43.450
We literally reinvent the wheel.

